# .dockerignore for mobius-chat Cloud Run build.
#
# Build context = /Users/ananth/Mobius (the parent of mobius-chat),
# because the Dockerfile COPYs sibling repos. So this file is consulted
# by docker-build for the parent tree, and we exclude everything that
# isn't one of the four sibling repos we actually vendor
# (mobius-chat, mobius-contracts, mobius-skills-core, mobius-retriever).
#
# Anything matched here never reaches the builder stage, so it can't
# bloat the final image and can't accidentally contain secrets.

# ── Default-exclude every sibling ────────────────────────────────────
# Allow-list pattern: exclude all directories under the build context,
# then un-exclude only the ones we need. This is safer than enumerating
# excluded siblings by name — new siblings in /Users/ananth/Mobius/
# are automatically excluded from chat's build.
*
!mobius-chat/
!mobius-contracts/
!mobius-skills-core/
!mobius-retriever/

# ── Within each vendored sibling, exclude noise ──────────────────────
# These patterns apply recursively regardless of which sibling; a
# .venv under mobius-contracts and one under mobius-chat are both
# stripped.

**/.git/
**/.github/
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/env/
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov/
**/*.egg-info/
**/build/
**/dist/

# ── Chat-specific development artifacts ──────────────────────────────
# tests/ is NOT shipped to prod — pytest is not in the runtime deps
# and tests carry fixtures that may leak PHI-shaped data.
mobius-chat/tests/
mobius-chat/docs/
mobius-chat/scripts/
mobius-chat/deploy/
mobius-chat/Dockerfile
mobius-chat/.dockerignore
mobius-chat/README.md
mobius-chat/notebooks/
mobius-chat/examples/
mobius-chat/.claude/

# node_modules in frontend/ if it exists — chat's frontend is
# vanilla HTML/JS today, but if a build step gets added, the
# node_modules artifact should not enter the image.
mobius-chat/frontend/node_modules/
mobius-chat/frontend/.next/
mobius-chat/frontend/dist/

# ── Sibling-package noise ─────────────────────────────────────────
# tests/ in the vendored packages aren't imported by chat; strip them
# to keep the image small.
mobius-contracts/tests/
mobius-skills-core/tests/
mobius-retriever/tests/

# ── Worktree / tooling noise ──────────────────────────────────────
**/.claude/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.DS_Store
